# Agentic systems (scoped)

When building AI/agent features:

1. Load skill `agentic-system-design`
2. Use **agent-patterns MCP** (`.cursor/mcp.json`) for recipes, symptoms, and catalog ids — see `mcp-architecture.mdc`
3. Hard cap on agent loop steps
4. Strict tool schemas; idempotent where retried
5. Human checkpoint before irreversible actions
6. Eval dataset before shipping user-facing agent behavior
7. Log model, tokens, latency, tool calls

Skills in repo for cloud: commit `.cursor/skills/` — global `~/.cursor/` does not sync.
